April 17, 2002

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2002-0266. Williams v. Hamilton Cty. Court of Common Pleas.

In Mandamus. On complaint in mandamus of Donald L. Williams, Sr. On S.Ct.Prac.R. X(5) determination, cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
